<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Generador de Sitemap.xml</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #6e8efb;
            --secondary: #a777e3;
            --dark: #2c3e50;
            --light: #f8f9fa;
            --success: #28a745;
            --danger: #dc3545;
            --warning: #ffc107;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: #333;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: var(--dark);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .description {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .instructions {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: var(--dark);
            margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary);
        }
        
        .instructions ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .instructions li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .url-list {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .url-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        .url-text {
            flex-grow: 1;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .result-container {
            margin-top: 30px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        pre {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-family: monospace;
            line-height: 1.5;
            max-height: 400px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #5a7df9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .btn-success {
            background-color: var(--success);
        }
        
        .btn-success:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
        
        .copy-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
        }
        
        .alert {
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: none;
        }
        
        .alert-success {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 30px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .url-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .url-text {
                margin-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Generador de Sitemap.xml</h1>
            <p class="description">Genera un sitemap.xml para tu sitio web en GitHub Pages con index.html y cv.html</p>
        </header>
        
        <div class="instructions">
            <h2><span class="step-number">1</span> Instrucciones</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Genera el contenido del sitemap.xml con el botón inferior</li>
                <li>Copia el contenido generado</li>
                <li>Crea un archivo llamado <code>sitemap.xml</code> en la raíz de tu repositorio</li>
                <li>Pega el contenido y haz commit</li>
                <li>Envía el sitemap a Google Search Console</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="url-list">
            <h2><span class="step-number">2</span> URLs que se incluirán en el sitemap</h2>
            <div class="url-item">
                <div class="url-text">https://rubencamargo.github.io/</div>
            </div>
            <div class="url-item">
                <div class="url-text">https://rubencamargo.github.io/cv.html</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="generateSitemap()">
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i> Generar Sitemap
            </button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="result-container" id="resultContainer" style="display: none;">
            <h2><span class="step-number">3</span> Tu Sitemap.xml</h2>
            <button class="btn copy-btn" onclick="copyToClipboard()">
                <i class="fas fa-copy"></i> Copiar
            </button>
            <pre id="sitemapOutput"></pre>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <h2><span class="step-number">4</span> Próximos pasos</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Copia el contenido anterior</li>
                    <li>Crea un archivo llamado <strong>sitemap.xml</strong> en la raíz de tu repositorio</li>
                    <li>Pega el contenido en el archivo y guárdalo</li>
                    <li>Haz commit y push a tu repositorio</li>
                    <li>Ve a Google Search Console → Sitemaps → Ingresa "sitemap.xml" → Enviar</li>
                </ol>
                
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <strong>URL de tu sitemap:</strong> 
                    <code id="sitemapUrl">https://rubencamargo.github.io/sitemap.xml</code>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function generateSitemap() {
            const today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
            
            const sitemapContent = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<urlset xmlns="http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9">
  <url>
    <loc>https://rubencamargo.github.io/</loc>
    <lastmod>${today}</lastmod>
    <changefreq>monthly</changefreq>
    <priority>1.0</priority>
  </url>
  <url>
    <loc>https://rubencamargo.github.io/cv.html</loc>
    <lastmod>${today}</lastmod>
    <changefreq>monthly</changefreq>
    <priority>0.8</priority>
  </url>
</urlset>`;
            
            document.getElementById('sitemapOutput').textContent = sitemapContent;
            document.getElementById('resultContainer').style.display = 'block';
            
            // Scroll to results
            document.getElementById('resultContainer').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
        }
        
        function copyToClipboard() {
            const sitemapContent = document.getElementById('sitemapOutput').textContent;
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(sitemapContent).then(() => {
                alert('¡Sitemap copiado al portapapeles!');
            }).catch(err => {
                console.error('Error al copiar: ', err);
            });
        }
        
        // Generate sitemap automatically when page loads
        window.onload = generateSitemap;
    </script>
</body>
</html>